11 An Act relating to counties and county officers;
amending 68 O.S. 2021, Section 1370.9, which relates
12 to lodging taxes levied by counties; permitting a
three percent lodging tax; clarifying that proceed
13 shall be used on county-owned facilities that promote
tourism; requiring vote before tax may be levied;
14 directing when a tax shall be effective; directing
for proceeds to be deposited into designated fund;
15 and providing an effective date.
