19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
20 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 68 O.S. 2021, Section 1370.9, is
21 amended to read as follows:
22 Section 1370.9. Lodging tax – Approval by voters – Designation
23 of purpose – Revolving funds.
